OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780966989
OL,3,CMay heatwave boosts spending on
OL,4,Cbarbecue food, sandals and sunglasses
OL,6,F"Getting new items into the suitcases
OL,7,Fof holidaymakers is also now key to
OL,8,Fthe summer performance of many
OL,9,Fretailers."
OL,11,FSeparate figures from Barclays show
OL,12,Fconsumer card spending grew 0.8% year
OL,13,Fon year in May, up from April's 0.1%
OL,14,Fdecline.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, the bank found consumer
OL,17,Fconfidence in the UK, European and
OL,18,Fglobal economies all rebounded,
OL,19,Freturning to levels seen at the
OL,20,Fbeginning of the year.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]
